project_descr: HOME AND AWAY: development and introduction of the innovative model in Lithuania aimed at mitigation of consequences of homelessness throughout the (re)integration into society and labour market

outputs.output_descr: Tailored model  is developed based on best EU practises and the assessment of  partner organisations' institutional capacities development needs; social workers representing 2 partner institutions trained on practical applications of  recommendations of the model, model is practically implemented in 2 project partners' organisations.
